OL,3,CTuchel has 'full choice' of players
OL,4,Cfor England's quarter-final against
OL,5,CNorway
OL,7,FDeclan Rice, Marc Guehi and Reece
OL,8,FJames have joined their England
OL,9,Fteammates for training, ahead of
OL,10,FEngland's World Cup quarter-final
OL,11,Fagainst Norway.
OL,13,FManager Thomas Tuchel said that meant
OL,14,Fhe had a "full choice" awaiting him
OL,15,Fwhen the lineup for Saturday's game is
OL,16,Fbeing decided.
OL,26,@vD@JOUvD@VO]
