PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783756130
OL,3,CTuchel has 'full choice' of players
OL,4,Cfor England's quarter-final against
OL,5,CNorway
OL,7,FAlthough England will be without
OL,8,Fdefender Jarell Quansah, as he begins
OL,9,Fserving his two-match suspension
OL,10,Ffollowing a red card, Rice, Guehi and
OL,11,FJames all went through training on
OL,12,FFriday at Inter Miami's facility, with
OL,13,Fco-owner David Beckham watching.
OL,15,FGuehi was reported to be suffering
OL,16,Ffrom a hamstring injury, while vice-
OL,17,Fcaptain Rice has been struck by a
OL,18,Fstomach bug, and James missed
OL,19,FEngland's last three matches with a
OL,20,Fhamstring issue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783756130
OL,3,CTuchel has 'full choice' of players
OL,4,Cfor England's quarter-final against
OL,5,CNorway
OL,7,FJordan Henderson was the only player
OL,8,Fto miss Friday's training, as he
OL,9,Fbegins his recovery from wrist surgery
OL,10,Ffollowing his fall during the
OL,11,Fcelebrations at the Estadio Azteca.
OL,13,FTuchel said: "We had everyone
OL,14,Favailable in training, which we of
OL,15,Fcourse like.
OL,17,F"We have the full choice except for
OL,18,Four suspended player Jarell Quansah,
OL,19,Fso that's the good news."
OL,26,@uD@NOUyD@AOU{D@YO]
