OL,3,CTuchel has 'full choice' of players
OL,4,Cfor England's quarter-final against
OL,5,CNorway
OL,7,FQuansah was given a two-match ban
OL,8,Ffollowing his red card against Mexico
OL,9,Fas it was deemed "serious foul play"
OL,10,Funder FIFA's disciplinary code.
OL,12,FThe versatile Bayer Leverkusen
OL,13,Fdefender was given a straight red
OL,14,Ffollowing a VAR review of his
OL,15,Fchallenge on Jesus Gallardo during the
OL,16,Fsecond half at the Azteca.
OL,26,@qD@ROUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
