PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783756130
OL,3,CTuchel has 'full choice' of players
OL,4,Cfor England's quarter-final against
OL,5,CNorway
OL,7,FAsked if he thought the extended ban
OL,8,Fmay have something to do with his
OL,9,Fcomments about the standard of
OL,10,Frefereeing after the Mexico game,
OL,11,FTuchel said: "I don't think so, but we
OL,12,Falso have no explanation."
